      "html": "<p>1853年，源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Japan \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Japan\">Japan</a> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -esque \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-esque\">-esque</a>。指受日本影响启发的美学。</p>"
    },
    {
